1. Export Compiled Binary in Arduino IDE
2. Rename File SuperSwitch_vXX.X.ino.bin
3. Replace existing .bin in the OTA Fireware Release folder on Main
4. Inside the new .bin file right click "Raw" and copy link.
5. Open Firmware_manifest.json
6. Update the version number.
7. Paste the Raw URL replacing the old URL
8. Write a firmware description that will display in the app.
